          "style_family": null,
          "text": "坐下，坐下。你能喝茶吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不用。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不用正好，我们这儿正没有开水呐。我说赵大爷，这野猫进宅，是无事不来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你今天怎么来了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，这是什么讲话？吾今日前来，要叫你替我打上一把钢刀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告便。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请便。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳呀，慢看。他前三年，打了一把刀，直到如今还没有给钱。今天又来打刀来"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啦。我可是不能再上他的当了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说赵大爷，你前三年还欠我们一把刀钱，没有给，今天再要打刀，但是一件。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪一件？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "现在我们铺子，搭上了伙计了。我自己不能作主，必须要同我们伙计商议商议。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但不知你的伙计是哪一个呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不瞒你能说，就是我的老婆。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么你的老婆又算是伙计了吓？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你没有听见人家常说吗：伙计伙计，如同夫妻；虽是夫妻，如同伙计。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤 吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "等我叫她出来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤 吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家里的，快出来呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吴妻上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴家生来命儿穷，嫁了个丈夫叫吴衍儿能。各样生意全不做，终朝打铁做营生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "当家的，深更半夜，你这么大惊小怪的，是什么事情吓？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他来啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他是谁呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赵匡胤，赵大爷来啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳，他不是死啦吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他没有死吓，活着呐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他到咱们这儿做什么来吓？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他要叫吾给他打一把刀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他既要打刀，你就该给他做了才是吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你别说啦，他前三年在咱们这儿打了一把刀，直到今日还没有钱给呐！谁还能"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再给他打呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那么你就把他打发走了去，就完了。你叫我出来做什么呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说我如今搭了伙计了，凡事要同伙计商量，我叫你出来，就说咱们这里生意"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不好，一切材料全用完了。他自然就走啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是这么一回事。好，走，咱们去见见他去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赵大爷，我伙计来了，你能有话，对她说罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说赵大爷，你能好吓？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好。我要奉求二位，给我打一把钢刀，不知你意下如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个……"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不行，不行，材料全用完了，连铁一点都没有了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "错得，铁是没有啦，门后头倒还有把刀枇子，似可以用得。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吴衍能使眼色调吴妻。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是什么居心呐？我说没有铁啦，你怎么说有刀枇子吓？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你真混蛋，你说是铁，我说是刀枇子，枇子是枇子，刀是刀！你真混蛋！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你才是混蛋，杂种！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王八蛋，杂种！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赵大爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，这是什么讲话？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虽然是有一把刀枇子，还是打不成。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎样还打不成呐？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "没有火怎么打？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "火虽没有，厨房里倒有一盏长命灯呐！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吴衍能使眼色调吴妻。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你真是“怀里端马勺——有点承心”。我说没有火，你为何说有灯吓？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你实在是混蛋！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你才是混蛋呐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你说的是火，我说的是灯。灯是灯，火是火。混蛋，"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能、吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杂种，王八蛋，"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赵大爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，又来了！既然有了火，又有刀枇子，你就与吾快快打起来才是吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请你到柜房里歇歇腿，待吾们给你能打起来就是了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "少陪了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵匡胤下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这分生意，你既是应承了，说不着，咱们就动起手来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吴衍能、吴妻拾椅子，点火。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "着了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "炉火本是老君留，"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "打铁磨钢鲁班修。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "三尺青锋定斩人头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "火又灭啦，待我再点起来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吴衍能点火。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又着了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "夫妻们终日受贫困，"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "每日里钉铁度光阴。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "但不知何日里才能安宁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "饥寒冻馁难扎挣"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来罢，打罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吴衍能持锤打椅，吴妻随打。吴妻哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳呀，我的天呐，我的天呐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你怎么哭起来啦？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你听听，打的声音，活像是钉棺材盖的声音，我怎么不哭吓？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你打铁都不知道门道吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳，这打铁还要什么门道？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这打铁必须要有一定的点儿，要打一个“定邦定，定邦定，定邦定邦定邦定”。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "敢自还有这些个讲究呐！来，咱们试演试演罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吴妻打。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "对啦，一点不错，打好啦，去搬石头去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "搬什么石头？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "搬那一块捶棒石。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那么大的石头，我可是搬不动。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你真白吃了饭啦！连一块石头都搬不动。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看那块石头，总有一二百斤。我要是能够搬得起来，我早去到黑寺里去拉劲"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "弓，托技勇，练弓刀石，去考武举去啦！我还同着你，在此受什么罪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你搬不动，你看我搬。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吴衍能搬石。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我也是搬不动。来罢，咱们两个人抬吧！先把火炉子抬开。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吴衍能、吴妻同抬椅，抬板橙，吴衍能骄橙磨刀。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去拿水去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，拿水去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吴妻持水碗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "往哪儿泼呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "头上。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吴妻用水泼吴衍能头。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，叫你往刀头上泼，你怎么往我头上泼起来啦？再去拿去！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，再拿去。往哪儿泼？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "往面上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "面上。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吴妻用水泼吴衍能面。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫你往刀面上，你怎么往人面上泼起来啦？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "等我再去拿去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "算了罢，就这头上滴搭下来的，就够用了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刀也打好了，有请赵大爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵匡胤上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刀可曾打好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打好了，你能拿去看看罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵匡胤接刀。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此刀甚好，但是吾身边分文未带，如何是好？有了，不免就将此二人开刀便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能、吴妻",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好良心！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吴衍能。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此刀甚好，你二人进前领赏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你赏罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看刀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵匡胤杀吴衍能、吴妻，二人背立。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看四下无人，不免就此逃走了罢！正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "双手拨开生死路，迈步跳出是非墙。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵匡胤下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走啦，好，好，把刀打好了，送给他，他倒把我们两口子杀啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你讲理不讲理呀？咱们叫他给杀死啦，你还在这里说什么话？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我这是鬼魂说话呐。咱们走吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上哪儿走吓？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴衍能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到阎王殿前去告他去！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "别挨骂啦，滚下去罢！"
        }
